SELECT DISTINCT 1 AS "a" FROM "catalogue_product" INNER JOIN "offer_rangeproduct" ON ("catalogue_product"."id" = "offer_rangeproduct"."product_id") WHERE ("offer_rangeproduct"."range_id" = 231 AND NOT (EXISTS(SELECT 1 AS "a" FROM "offer_range_excluded_products" U1 WHERE (U1."range_id" = 231 AND U1."product_id" = ("catalogue_product"."id")) LIMIT 1)) AND "catalogue_product"."id" = 140) LIMIT 1
